## Building a system
To build a functional system, you'll need the following:
- Program 1 ESP8266 or ESP32 with the code located in espnow_gateway
- Program 1 eSP8266 or ESP32 with the code located in espnow_sensor.
- HW for sensor.
-- Connect RTS to D1  (to be able to wake up from deep sleepfor deep sleep to obe able to wake up
You can run this unit on USB-5v or a battery. If using a battery you can alos  230V (mains) shouls also  the Set ing syste
